# Input

```svelte
{#each categories as category}
  <div class="category">
    <h2>{category.name}</h2>
    {#each category.items as item, i}
      <div class="item">{i}: {item.title}</div>
    {/each}
  </div>
{/each}

{#each matrix as row}
  {#each row as cell}
    <span>{cell}</span>
  {/each}
{/each}

```


# Formatted

```svelte
{#each categories as category}
	<div class="category">
		<h2>{category.name}</h2>
		{#each category.items as item, i}
			<div class="item">{i}: {item.title}</div>
		{/each}
	</div>
{/each}

{#each matrix as row}
	{#each row as cell}
		<span>{cell}</span>
	{/each}
{/each}

```
